descriptionMarkdown:
Simple red-yellow-green indicator unit.

Default blueprint indicate light oil level in such ranges:
- 0....25k units - Red light
- 25k...50k units - Yellow light
- 50k+ units - Green light

1. Set the link between the inputs of the arithmetic combinator (A) in upper-left corner and storage.
2. Set type of fluid/item indication on this (A) arithmetic combinator.
3. Set values of indication ranges on two decider combinators below (B and C, see figure)

Notice, that number [0] and settings [>=] on decider combinator (D) in lower-left corner must stay untochable to proper work of the red indicaton range of the scheme.
title: 3-phase light indicator
